OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1774335860
OL,3,CRoyal Mail investigating after piles
OL,4,Cof unopened letters found in recycling
OL,5,Cbin
OL,7,FA resident spoke to ITV Central
OL,8,Fcorrespondent Mark Gough about their
OL,9,Fshock at discovering mail in the bin
OL,11,FRoyal Mail is investigating after a
OL,12,Fhuge pile of unopened mail was
OL,13,Fdiscovered in a recycling bin in
OL,14,FSaltley in Birmingham.
OL,16,FThe letters were addressed to people
OL,17,Fliving nearby and were from banks,
OL,18,Futility companies, and the NHS.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/3
