PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1774335860
OL,3,CRoyal Mail investigating after piles
OL,4,Cof unopened letters found in recycling
OL,5,Cbin
OL,7,FMichael, whose mother found them in
OL,8,Fher recycling bin, said, "We really
OL,9,Fdidn't know what to do. I was a bit
OL,10,Foverwhelmed with the amount of letters
OL,11,Fto be honest."
OL,13,FOne of the letters is dated as being
OL,14,Fposted on 27th January.
OL,16,FRoyal Mail said in a statement, "The
OL,17,Fsafety and security of the mail is
OL,18,Fextremely important to us, and we take
OL,19,Fincidents like this very seriously.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/3
