OL,3,CRoyal Mail investigating after piles
OL,4,Cof unopened letters found in recycling
OL,5,Cbin
OL,7,F"The local delivery office is
OL,8,Finvestigating and will take
OL,9,Fappropriate action, including working
OL,10,Fto address any affected items."
